        "executionId": "call_G069jtiNieE0IbeC7D2jDGFG",
        "result": {
          "success": true,
          "data": "### Café Menu\n\n**Target Demographic:**\nThe target demographic for our new café includes health-conscious individuals, young professionals, students, and families looking for a cozy spot to enjoy quality food and beverages. The menu emphasizes fresh, organic, and locally sourced ingredients, aligning with current food trends such as plant-based options, artisanal flavors, and sustainable practices.\n\n---\n\n#### Beverage Options\n\n1. **Cold Brew Coffee with Oat Milk**\n   - **Description:** Smooth and rich cold brew coffee made from ethically sourced beans, served over ice with creamy oat milk, and a hint of vanilla syrup.\n   - **Price Range:** $4.00 - $5.50\n\n2. **Matcha Latte (Iced or Hot)**\n   - **Description:** Organic Japanese matcha whisked to perfection, blended with steamed milk (dairy or plant-based options) for a vibrant and energizing drink.\n   - **Price Range:** $5.00 - $6.50\n\n3. **Berry Hibiscus Iced Tea**\n   - **Description:** A refreshing blend of hibiscus tea infused with mixed berries, served chilled with a splash of sparkling water and garnished with fresh mint.\n   - **Price Range:** $3.50 - $4.50\n\n---\n\n#### Dessert Options\n\n1. **Vegan Chocolate Avocado Mousse**\n   - **Description:** A rich and creamy dessert made with ripe avocados, dark cocoa powder, and maple syrup, topped with crushed nuts and fresh berries. This indulgent yet healthy treat is gluten-free and dairy-free.\n   - **Price Range:** $6.00 - $7.50\n\n2. **Mini Almond Flour Lemon Tart**\n   - **Description:** A zesty lemon tart made with almond flour crust, filled with a luscious lemon curd and topped with a dollop of coconut whipped cream. Perfectly sweet and tart, it’s a gluten-free option that delights the palate.\n   - **Price Range:** $5.50 - $7.00\n\n---\n\n### Summary\n\nThis café menu is designed to cater to the needs and preferences of our target audience by offering a blend of health-conscious beverages and desserts that reflect current food trends. Each item is priced competitively to ensure accessibility while maintaining high-quality ingredients and flavor profiles."
